article:
The long-running science fiction television series 'Doctor Who' has over the
years been the subject of many comedy sketches and specially made comedy
programmes, from Spike Milligan's "Pakistani Dalek" to the Comic Relief episode
[[Doctor Who and the Curse of Fatal Death]]. There have been occasional parodies
and references to Doctor Who on American TV shows such as [[Saturday Night
Live]], [[The Simpsons]], [[Community]], [[Late Night with Conan O'Brien]],
[[Robot Chicken]], and [[The Colbert Report]]. What follows below is a
